Unitron/Anubis/Hades:




Unitron sighed.  He, and Anubis and Hades had been waiting for an hour or 
two, not getting a reply from the Maximals.  That was annoying.

Unitron activated his comm. unit, sending a transmission to the Ark.  

<This is Unitron, of Koga Shuko's soldiers.  We've brought you your fifty 
kilos of liquid energon in tribute!  Come down and get it, or are you waiting 
until the cease fire is up so you can shoot us!?>
